tar structure
	tar {create|extract} [options] <name_of_archive> <source file|directory>
to archive -z gzip_compression -j bzip_compression -c create_archive -v verbose -f file
	tar -zcvf hints.tar.gz hints/
to extract -x and decompress -z
	tar -zxvf hints.tar.gz
-C relative path names and . to make a backup of the current directory
	tar cvf -C hint.tar hints/ .
to move content of directory to another
	tar -cC /old . | tar -xC /new









